<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Error al Registrarse o Iniciar Sesi칩n</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="error.css">
    <link rel="icon" href="/esaw/vid-user-logo-defaul/zypherr(1).png">

</head>
<body>
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@400;700&display=swap');

        body {
            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            height: 100vh;
            background: linear-gradient(120deg, #1e1e2e 0%, #16283d 100%);
            color: #ecf0f1;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .error-container {
            text-align: center;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px;
            padding: 40px;
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.068);
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0px 15px 30px rgba(22, 4, 51, 0.5);
            animation: fadeIn 1s ease-in-out;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #3498db;
            font-size: 3.5em;
            margin: 0;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            text-shadow: 3px 3px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
        }

        p {
            color: #bdc3c7;
            font-size: 1.2em;
            margin-top: 20px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .image-container {
            margin-top: 30px;
        }

        img {
            filter: grayscale(50%) sepia(30%) contrast(1.2);
            width: 250px;
            height: auto;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
        }

        a {
            color: #3498db;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            margin-top: 20px;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        a:hover {
            color: #1abc9c;
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            background-color: #3498db;
            color: white;
            font-size: 1.2em;
            font-weight: bold;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0px 6px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .button:hover {
            background-color: #2980b9;
            transform: translateY(-4px);
        }

        /* Animations */
        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(-20px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }
    </style>

    <div class="error-container">
        <h1>Oops!</h1>
        <p id="errorMessage">Algo sali칩 mal al intentar registrarte o iniciar sesi칩n. Por favor, intenta nuevamente.</p>
        <div class="image-container">
            <img src="/esaw/vid-user-logo-defaul/zypherr.png" alt="Zypher Error Logo">
        </div>
        <p>Vuelve a <a href="/">la p치gina de inicio</a> o contacta con soporte si el error persiste.</p>
        <a href="/" class="button">Volver al Inicio</a>
    </div>

    <script src="/asdf2/errorlog/script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
